SUMMARY:Friday Fusion in TIGARD
DESCRIPTION:FRIDAY NIGHT DANCING IN TIGARD\nKnown as our popular Friday Fusion Social! \nHeating up 3 DANCE FLOORS & jam packed evening with something for everyone featuring Country & Latin styles! \nBEGINNING LESSONS\, 3 ROOMS\, Full bar\, food options and tons of FUN! This is the perfect date night or the perfect place to meet someone new! Lots of singles come\, so no partner needed! No experience or special shoes needed! Come enjoy an awesome night at this huge facility with dancing all night and over 500 people in attendance! \nDOORS OPEN 7:30PM\nBEG LESSONS at 7:45PM & 8:30PM\n​Open to couples and singles\, groups of friends!\nCome meet new people and have a BLAST! \n*LESSON & ROOM SCHEDULE POSTED CLOSER TO EVENT* \nOPEN TO THE PUBLIC:\nCover $15/person\nIncludes ALL rooms & lessons – WOW! \n*Included in All Access Membership \nCome as you are – ALL are welcome!\nAges 18+\nProfessional security on site.\nNo outside food or drink allowed\nPersonal water canteens allowed empty through doors.\nFree water inside. \nQuestions? Call: 503.624.6565
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/friday-night-dancing-in-tigard/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Shawn Gardner Dancing\, 8900 SW Commercial St.\, Tigard\, OR\, 97223\, US
CATEGORIES:Portland
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/605638354_1447289617404459_8156949349380033734_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
