SUMMARY:GUAD Latin Dance Social!
DESCRIPTION:Once a month\, we all get together in the Get Up and Dance Studio for a fun night of Latin dancing! This event will be specially DJ’d by DJ Vic with all the best Latin music\, and we will celebrate the love of dance together. \nYou will hear music being played to represent all of your favorite Latin dances\, including SALSA\, BACHATA\, and CHA CHA CHA! Starting with a fiery salsa class at 8 p.m\, no pre-registration required\, and no partner necessary. \nOnly $10/per person total for the class\, or $12 for the social\, if you attend both\, it’s only $15! It’s a social for everyone\, regardless of level of experience. Plenty of parking\, BYOB\, and bring your ready-to-dance selves!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/guad-may-latin-dance-social/2026-03-27/
LOCATION:Get Up And Dance\, 1810 Water Place\, suite 250\, Atlanta\, GA\, United States
CATEGORIES:Atlanta
END:VEVENT
