DESCRIPTION:Warm up your Friday nights with some salsa at The Collaroy. Come and learn the basics or show off your moves. We’ve got free salsa classes every Friday from 8pm – 9pm and $15 cocktail happy hour from 9pm – 11pm to get you in the fiesta mood. \nWith live percussion and DJs playing Latin party tunes\, reggaetón and Bossa Nova until late\, you’re guaranteed a fun night. So put on your dancing shoes and get ready to Rumba!
